reviewText: The video quality is not as video perfect as I expected. Its alright though because I'm after to learn the techniques after all.

First of all the videos I recieved were not even the ones advertised. It was the same Martial Arts style but not the Martial Artist. Second, one dvd didn't even work. :(  I'm not returning them, it's to much of a waste of time. I was very dissapointed in Amazon, who has been very very good to me.
